Subject: [PATCH 2/2] mmc: cavium: Set the correct dma max segment size

The dma max segment size of PCI device is set to 64K by default in
function pci_device_add(). So when we set the dma max segment size
for the mmc host, we should consider this limitation. Otherwise we
would get a calltrace like below when the CONFIG_DMA_API_DEBUG_SG
is enabled.
